{"tid":1656183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］仲有極多其他CCTV可以拎","createTime":"2019-10-15T12:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T16:23:51.000Z","uid":264368,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1e74c8b0eff4c349772f2ee8f0bf0f3dcfcbfae3","tid":1656183,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WB9OHvf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWB9OHvf.png&h=63544cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅色：跟據學校CCTV 及 目擊者證據之路線<br />\n黃色：往海旁唯一路線<br />\n藍色：有CCTV覆蓋範圍<br />\n綠色：大量巴士往巴士總站之路線<br />\n<br />\nA：停車場CCTV <br />\n- 56，57，56嗰段<br />\n<br />\nB：地鐵站內店舖CCTV<br />\n- 有目擊者琴晚開post以及今日現身HKDI聲稱目擊陳同學由02舖行至10舖 （A出口往HKDI）<br />\n- 藍色：目測有對住舖外既CCTV<br />\n09-10 盈健醫務中心 11 太子餅點 12-13 爭鮮 14 OK便利店 15 美心西餅 16 裝修中 08 中銀櫃員機 <span style=\"color: blue;\"> 07 HKTV Mall </span> 06 QB House <span style=\"color: blue;\">05 恒生櫃員機</span> 04 東海堂 03 波仔 02 鴻福堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/118f6W6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F118f6W6.jpg&h=23b0bd0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC：工地CCTV<br />\n- 安裝位置較高，未能確認CCTV對住既方向<br />\n<br />\nD：獨立屋外圍CCTV<br />\n- 每隔大約50米就有一部，可以極清楚睇到去海旁既每一個人<br />\n<br />\n大多數CCTV只keep一個月，時間緊逼<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可否考慮眾籌，買起啲CCTV片段，買得幾多得幾多</span><br />\n<br />\n本人熱愛生命，絕不自殺。"},{"pid":"e2dd8d34294d0efc99d3ff8b6f9d6c823c4143fc","tid":1656183,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277c6ba925e27a4f94f946305da40b5b5a7ba4cd","tid":1656183,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:52:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caa07489cdf2c05d78f9e38cadae72f1ec0bf47f","tid":1656183,"uid":